    <div class="container">
        <a href="https://tech.petalbe.com" class="back-link">← Back to Petalbe Technologies</a>
        
        <h1>Privacy Policy for Mera</h1>
        
        <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: February 13, 2025</p>

        <div class="intro">
            <p><strong>Your privacy matters.</strong> Mera is designed with privacy at its core. We process all your vocabulary and learning data locally on your device using Apple's secure infrastructure. We don't collect, sell, or share your personal information with third parties for marketing or advertising purposes.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="privacy-badge">
            <p style="margin: 0;"><strong>✓ Privacy-First Design</strong></p>
            <p style="margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 0;">All vocabulary processing happens locally on your device. Your data syncs securely through Apple's iCloud using your Apple ID. We never see your personal learning data.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
            <p><strong>Service Provider:</strong> Petalbe Technologies<br>
            <strong>Owner:</strong> Bianca Scholze<br>
            <strong>Contact:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@petalbe.com">privacy@petalbe.com</a></p>
            <p>Mera is a Hindi vocabulary learning app for iOS that helps you build conversational Hindi skills through personalized exercises and spaced repetition.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>2. Data We Collect</h2>
            
            <h3>2.1 Vocabulary Data</h3>
            <p>When you use Mera, the following data is stored locally on your device:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Vocabulary Items:</strong> Hindi words, English translations, parts of speech, categories, example sentences, and notes that you add or upload</li>
                <li><strong>Learning Progress:</strong> Your mastery level, correct/incorrect answer counts, review dates, and spaced repetition schedules for each vocabulary item</li>
                <li><strong>Exercise Statistics:</strong> Exercise completion data, scores, accuracy rates, and time spent practicing</li>
                <li><strong>User Preferences:</strong> Daily goals, notification settings, and app configuration choices</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>Storage Location:</strong> All this data is stored locally using Apple's Core Data framework on your device. If you enable iCloud sync, this data is automatically synchronized across your Apple devices via CloudKit.</p>
            
            <h3>2.2 Apple ID Information</h3>
            <p>Mera uses your Apple ID for iCloud sync functionality. We do not collect or store your Apple ID credentials. Apple handles all authentication securely.</p>
            
            <h3>2.3 What We Don't Collect</h3>
            <p>We explicitly <strong>do not collect</strong>:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Personal identification information (name, email, phone number) beyond your Apple ID for sync</li>
                <li>Location data or GPS coordinates</li>
                <li>Device identifiers for advertising purposes</li>
                <li>Browsing history or activity outside the app</li>
                <li>Contacts, photos, or other sensitive device data</li>
                <li>Payment information (handled entirely by Apple)</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
            
            <h3>3.1 Purpose of Data Processing</h3>
            <p>Your vocabulary and learning data is used exclusively to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Personalize Your Learning:</strong> Track which words you've mastered, which need review, and optimize spaced repetition schedules</li>
                <li><strong>Generate Exercises:</strong> Create personalized flashcards, quizzes, and practice sessions based on your learning history</li>
                <li><strong>Display Progress:</strong> Show your learning statistics, streaks, mastery levels, and achievements</li>
                <li><strong>Sync Across Devices:</strong> Keep your vocabulary and progress synchronized across all your Apple devices via iCloud</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>3.2 Local Processing</h3>
            <p>All vocabulary processing, exercise generation, and progress calculations happen <strong>entirely on your device</strong>. When you upload CSV files with vocabulary, they are parsed locally without sending data to external servers.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>4. Data Storage and Security</h2>
            
            <h3>4.1 Core Data and CloudKit</h3>
            <p>Mera uses Apple's Core Data framework for local storage and CloudKit for optional iCloud synchronization. Both are industry-standard technologies with built-in encryption and security measures.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Local Storage:</strong> Data is stored in an encrypted SQLite database managed by Core Data</li>
                <li><strong>iCloud Sync:</strong> When enabled, data syncs via CloudKit using end-to-end encryption</li>
                <li><strong>Access Control:</strong> Only you can access your data through your Apple ID. We (Petalbe Technologies) cannot access your iCloud data</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>4.2 Data Retention</h3>
            <p>Your data remains on your device and in your iCloud account until you choose to delete it. We do not have access to delete your data on our behalf.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
            
            <h3>5.1 Apple Services</h3>
            <p>Mera relies exclusively on Apple's infrastructure:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Apple ID:</strong> For user authentication and iCloud sync (Apple's Privacy Policy applies)</li>
                <li><strong>CloudKit:</strong> For cross-device data synchronization (covered by Apple's iCloud Terms)</li>
                <li><strong>TestFlight:</strong> For beta testing, which collects anonymized crash reports and usage analytics handled by Apple</li>
                <li><strong>App Store:</strong> For app distribution and in-app purchases (Apple's standard terms apply)</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Apple's Privacy Policy: <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/</a></p>
            
            <h3>5.2 No Advertising or Analytics</h3>
            <p>Mera does <strong>not</strong> use:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Third-party analytics services (no Google Analytics, Facebook Pixel, etc.)</li>
                <li>Advertising networks or tracking SDKs</li>
                <li>Social media integration that shares your data</li>
                <li>External servers for data processing or storage</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>6. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
            
            <h3>6.1 Access and Control</h3>
            <p>You have complete control over your data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>View Your Data:</strong> All your vocabulary and progress is visible within the app's Library and Statistics sections</li>
                <li><strong>Edit Your Data:</strong> You can edit or delete individual vocabulary items at any time</li>
                <li><strong>Export Your Data:</strong> You can export your vocabulary data in standard formats (future feature)</li>
                <li><strong>Delete All Data:</strong> Delete the app to remove all local data. For iCloud data, manage it through your Apple ID settings</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>6.2 iCloud Data Management</h3>
            <p>To manage your iCloud data:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Go to iPhone Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Manage Storage → Mera</li>
                <li>You can disable iCloud sync or delete iCloud data from here</li>
                <li>Deleting iCloud data will not affect local data stored on your device</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h3>6.3 Right to Be Forgotten</h3>
            <p>Since we do not collect personal data on our servers, simply deleting the app removes all local data. For iCloud data, use Apple's iCloud management tools as described above.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>7. Children's Privacy</h2>
            <p>Mera is suitable for users of all ages, including children under 13. However, we do not knowingly collect personal information from children. Since all data is stored locally and synced via Apple's infrastructure, parents should review Apple's Family Sharing and parental controls for managing children's app usage.</p>
            <p>If a parent or guardian believes their child has provided data to Mera in a manner inconsistent with this policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@petalbe.com">privacy@petalbe.com</a>.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>8. International Data Transfers</h2>
            <p>Mera processes all data locally on your device. If you enable iCloud sync, your data is stored in Apple's iCloud infrastructure, which may involve international data transfers according to Apple's policies. Apple complies with applicable data protection laws including GDPR for European users.</p>
            <p>For more information on Apple's data transfer mechanisms, visit: <a href="https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://www.apple.com/legal/privacy/</a></p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>9. Data Breach Notification</h2>
            <p>Since we do not collect or store your data on our servers, the risk of a data breach affecting your Mera data is minimal. Your data security depends on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Your device's security (passcode, Face ID, Touch ID)</li>
                <li>Your Apple ID security (two-factor authentication recommended)</li>
                <li>Apple's iCloud security infrastructure</li>
            </ul>
            <p>If Apple notifies us of any security incident affecting Mera users, we will promptly inform affected users according to applicable legal requirements.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>10. Legal Basis for Processing (GDPR)</h2>
            <p>For users in the European Economic Area (EEA), United Kingdom, and Switzerland, we process your data based on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Contractual Necessity (Art. 6(1)(b) GDPR):</strong> Processing vocabulary and progress data is essential to provide the app's core learning functionality</li>
                <li><strong>Legitimate Interest (Art. 6(1)(f) GDPR):</strong> Storing user preferences and settings to improve user experience</li>
                <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Where applicable, such as enabling optional iCloud sync features</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>11. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
            <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, technology, or legal requirements. When we make significant changes, we will:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Update the "Last Updated" date at the top of this policy</li>
                <li>Notify you through the app (for material changes)</li>
                <li>Request your consent if required by applicable law</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We encourage you to review this policy periodically. Continued use of Mera after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>12. Contact Us</h2>
            <p>If you have questions, concerns, or requests regarding this privacy policy or your data, please contact us:</p>
            <p>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@petalbe.com">privacy@petalbe.com</a><br>
                <strong>Company:</strong> Petalbe Technologies<br>
                <strong>Website:</strong> <a href="https://tech.petalbe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://tech.petalbe.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>We will respond to your inquiry within 30 days.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-block">
            <h2>13. Supervisory Authority</h2>
            <p>If you are located in the EEA, UK, or Switzerland and believe we have not addressed your privacy concerns adequately, you have the right to lodge a complaint with your local data protection authority.</p>
        </div>

